<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.8">
<l>iravu kūrntiruḷ perukiya varaimuḻai</l>
<l>yirumpaci yatukūra</l>
<l>arava māvikku  makaṉpoḻil taḻuviya</l>
<l>varuvarai yimayattu</l>
<l>parama ṉātiyem paṉimukil vaṇṇaṉeṉ</l>
<l>ṟeṇṇiniṉ ṟimaiyōrkaḷ</l>
<l>pirama ṉōṭuceṉ ṟaṭitoḻum peruntakaip</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the Himalayas with harsh peaks embraced by broad forests</l>
<l rend="indent">where a serpent sighs as its great hunger increases</l>
<l>In a mountain cave, where the night, thickening, expands the darkness,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti of the [one of] great propriety</l>
<l rend="indent">where the unblinking [celestials] and Brahmā</l>
<l rend="indent">come and worship at [his] feet,</l>
<l>Meditating continually, saying, “Supreme! Primal [lord]!</l>
<l rend="indent">our cool cloud-hued one!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
